                    Our quizzes are based on validated assessment tools used by healthcare professionals worldwide.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="bi bi-brain"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="feature-title">Personalized Results</h3>
                <p class="feature-description">
                    Get tailored recommendations based on your assessment results and health profile.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="bi bi-lock"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="feature-title">Private & Secure</h3>
                <p class="feature-description">
                    Your health data is encrypted, secure, and never shared without your explicit consent.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="bi bi-lightning"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="feature-title">Quick Assessments</h3>
                <p class="feature-description">
                    Complete your quizzes in just a few minutes and get instant results and recommendations.
